{"tid":1554552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[防暴夜襲公屋邨]葵涌邨96發生的事","createTime":"2019-09-09T04:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T01:05:06.000Z","uid":237249,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"75e8b227fde718690d1eb90ef5183e9ef48e74f2","tid":1554552,"uid":237249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"因為個晚焦點係太子所以唔想轉移焦點依家先po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事源係個晚有藍絲打人 街坊圍人 藍絲報警<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗車晨早到但無落車</span></span> 之後救護車到左 送走藍絲上白車<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救護走左之後啲人開始散 啲狗就開始落車黎料 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞棍跑入邨驅散市民 好多後生入左雅葵樓<br />\n然後班狗入埋雅葵 係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">電梯位</span></span>等人查人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有傳有入後樓梯</span></span><br />\n之後仲守住前後門叫人入密碼先好入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/0dbfh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F0dbfh&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=bcc86b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/0dbfh</a><br />\n<br />\n講返件事係想各位小心 知道之後同類事件好易發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次見到藍絲打人拿拿林私了然後散仲好"},{"pid":"39561bae507db11b664ab75a5ea34214abd07e59","tid":1554552,"uid":237249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51895a7d8bafc6de59780bbfb655981635af9c02","tid":1554552,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"[高質國際文宣]全世界同我入黎轉發<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554494</a>"},{"pid":"3a251793ad024ac1eb2af745655c6a05a55dfb11","tid":1554552,"